Label: has qualitative result
definition: A relation between an experiment and a result

Label: has source organism
definition: A relation between a compound or substance and its producing organism

Label: has compound
definition: A relation between a substance and a compound

Label: has identified compound
definition: A relation between a substance and a compound in which the compound has been identified

Label: has isolated compound
definition: A relation between a substance and a compound in which the compound has been isolated at least once

Label: has a lack of compound
definition: A relation between a substance and the absence  (or below the limit of detection) of a compound in it
